Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 绘瑠是这么报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过去跟他说说话会不会好点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得先放他一段时间比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来受伤很重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是想要让司打起精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你真的向艾拉告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你… 那个… 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司真的向你告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我听说你拒绝他了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被告 告 告白了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你完全看起来不像没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}脑子里跳出了许多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺势就告诉他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后司就一直那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我向他搭话似乎也听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他那样子不管谁去搭话都一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是艾拉需要在意的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该说司最近有些得意忘形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会变成这样肯定大概就是他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是不会看气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然就跑出来告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和司在嘉年华会场上走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看吧果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连好好保护女生都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他非常拚命地找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 这是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后就开始放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们一起牵着手看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那时候牵手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不错…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后顺着话题就被抱住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是激情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一点都不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定要拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也会那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我伤害了司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉想怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是满会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得就算你问她也没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满又没有被人告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}够了 别在那多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在司面前你还能像以前一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想两个人都应该先冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要试试跟司分开过几天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话你也可以好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对他到底是怎样的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具体怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…现在正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来你没有计划啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的目标需要小心一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者引起过暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有前科的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说…你知道司向艾拉告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么！ 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司求婚时说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是求婚 是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个家伙 进展到什么程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说进展…是指的什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概…知道你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉似乎拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拒绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的表情很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闭嘴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是擅自动房间的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不会轻易饶过你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是司做了任何一点可疑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把他赶出房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满的内衣放在这边的抽屉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告诉他干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 为什么我和司住一间房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在的司气氛那么沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂且忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男生和女生换一下房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要和绘瑠一起照顾艾拉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安慰司就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用做到那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算消沉到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我爽快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被甩掉而已有什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正不理你 你也只会坐在那里什么都不吃发呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我的房间饿死了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么觉得一晚上不吃不喝也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃吧 趁着还没有凉快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁着还没有凉赶快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比…比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么你给我穿这件衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉竟然会来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梦想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全冷静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克 太不象话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不认真工作却一心搞职场恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区一个新人太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是现在还把自己当学生的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我无话可说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要把工作和私生活分开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在像你这样的废柴 去回收和家人一样的吉芙提尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别人会怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你说过我爸爸变成游荡者的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我眼睁睁的失去父亲 变成孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然香月姐来看过我很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就对她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「你不用再来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为吉芙提尔和持有者提供心灵依靠是终端服务的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我虽然不能代替你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是至少能陪你说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你振作起来之前希望你让我这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然我没办法面对你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到那样的香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才想加入终端服务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我为自己在这里工作感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以如果你在这里混日子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我饶不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我只是作为一个前辈指导你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告白之后后悔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然被拒绝了 但是对艾拉的感情不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还挺执着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得你这点很帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为…为什么我刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说你真的懂我在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂的话就别在那里发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好想想今后怎么和艾拉接触
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\fs37}真的是爱管闲事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什么了说出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会听着的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 今晚不会让你睡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来开睡衣派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下就会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那个 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了艾拉拉我准备了这么多的睡衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从哪个开始穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 从哪个开始？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恶 没想到竟然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不快点准备的话要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么不早点叫我起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总觉得…有点怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是我该在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 我们并没有做什么下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系 司和满很般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 要赶快追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解开了误会真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我太冲动弄错了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 要怪也怪我没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别不说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易有这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好聊一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我那时候拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再给我一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是无论艾拉作何决断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请至少让我继续做你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什么在意的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得恋爱是不是气势也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是指艾拉的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我让那孩子好好考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种事花费太多时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会向着坏的方向考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…究竟怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是什么茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你实际上是怎么看待司的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么司总是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一开始让我在意的是这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前满不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司可能是因为悲伤而笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想让他有那样的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总想着要帮他些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是去游乐园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从中途心就怦怦地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一想到司的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心里就充满紧张和悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没办法用语言来形容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗是吗 果然是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经得到答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自己也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 答案早已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然 那就赶快去和司说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2\fs38}我要离开司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下 你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得这样做对彼此都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话我就跟你明说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你感觉到的这种悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是恋爱 是恋爱的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以根本不需要离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更要远离司了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不懂 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样才能得出这样的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为…一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我只剩下大概一个月的寿命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 你居然没喝醉真是罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别那么瞪着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是嫌我碍事的话 我会自动消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是不是煽动司了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煽动什么的 太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只是自己想清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像个男人一样表达出自己的心意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果就是那个德行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们俩好不容易才合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么你是打算干涉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然至今一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有这种时候才会装得像个前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这人对于可爱的后辈的事情可是一清二楚的哟
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在这种地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉寿命的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你什么时候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明明什么都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却对你和艾拉尽说些自作聪明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明应该在工作上已经适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说是最近才知道寿命的事的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在告白之前 还是之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 你是明明知道还去告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做了这个工作以后 到底都看到了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分手是注定的 而你为什么还要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想创造和艾拉在一起的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想为艾拉创造回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 我也想为她做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要做的是非常痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能会有什么好结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 你也能毫不退缩地面对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我在爸爸的那时候逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没能面对他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此伤害了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能够负责到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经决定 要一直做艾拉的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直到最后的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}责任的意义 你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和那时的我完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这样我才说外行完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在说你是个无药可救的恋爱新手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我就稍微支持一下你们的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好谢谢我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么你会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我被香月叫了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今天起 你们两个解除搭档关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没听清楚吗 解除搭档关系
